data.description: Please read broker remarks regarding an assumable loan at 3.25%.  Raised 3 bedroom 2 full bath ranch in Turkeyfoot Heights.  Finished recreation room with a 2 car attached garage.  Eat in kitchen area, (pantry), Inground pool, fenced backyard, walking distance to Turkeyfoot Heights park, recreation amenities including tennis/pickleball courts, lake access, boat docks, basketball, picnic area, and more thru the HOA. All the pool equipment is located in the shed in back, newer dolphin automatic pool cleaner.  The concrete had both skimmers replaced as well as repainting the pool.  Furnace in 2018, waterproofing in 2018, all appliances stay.  Minutes from Portage Lakes State Park.
